SIMPLE: unembodied
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unembodied
<hw>Un`em*bod"ied</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Free
from a corporeal body; disembodied; <as>as, <ex>unembodied</ex>
spirits</as>.</def> <rj><au>Byron.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not embodied; not collected into a body; not yet
organized; <as>as, <ex>unembodied</ex> militia</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unempirically</ent>⟦br⟧
